A Ghana-based pastor, Prophet Nigel Gaisie, has revealed that Nigeria’s Vice President, Yemi Osinbajo will become president in 2021. Gaisie, who is the founder of the Prophetic Hill Chapel Prophet made the prediction during his crossover service on Thursday, BBC reports. “Nigeria’s Vice President Yemi Osinbajo will become president,” he said. Prophet Gaisie also predicted trouble in the Ashanti Kingdom of Ghana. He said: “I saw darkness around the Ashanti kingdom.” The prophet assured of peace on the international scene. He also predicted that a famous preacher would die in 2021. “The world will enjoy peace, but America will have a terrorist attack,” he said.